snippet.title: PC Engine Longplay [274] Bikkuriman World
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

This is one of the two PC Engine launch titles (the other is Shanghai).

It's Wonderboy in Monster Land! And it's a very nice looking game (for 1987), better than some that are to be released in the later years. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
